# Build context hygiene for Dockerfile.api / Dockerfile.worker (context = backend/).
# Keep host build output, IDE state, and VCS metadata OUT of the image build context — they bloat the
# context transfer, can leak local state, and (critically) a stale host bin/obj of a different SDK/RID
# would confuse `dotnet restore`/`publish` inside the linux build container.
**/bin
**/obj
**/.vs
**/.idea
**/*.user
**/.DS_Store
**/TestResults
**/*.log
.git
.gitignore
.dockerignore
Dockerfile.*
